        <note>I accept RM's reading of the received text, which he prints as clear. In the published estampage it is very much unclear; I cannot see a subscript <foreign>ś</foreign> at all, though compare line 23 above. RM emends the name to Bhavaśarman, but I prefer not to do so.</note>
